column4: FotoNation is a technology company focused on providing innovative and efficient solutions through ultra-low power embedded hardware and accelerated edge-AI technologies. The company aims to enhance signal quality and enable advanced AI analytics. FotoNation's products allow System on Chip (SoC) makers to integrate high-quality neural signal processing and analytics into their chips through IP-Core and Chiplet technologies. Through their commitment to innovation, they cater to a range of markets and continually strive to deliver cutting-edge solutions that optimize performance and functionality.

Carlin Consumer Health specializes in the development and management of over-the-counter health and beauty brands. The company leverages long-standing connections and a strong voice with major and regional retailers to ensure that their products receive the attention they deserve in the market. They focus on fulfilling the unique needs of established healthcare brands while optimizing their presence in retail.

column3: ['Ultra-Low Power Embedded Hardware', 'Edge-AI Solutions', 'Neural Signal Processing', 'AI Analytics']
column4: FotoNation is a technology company specializing in ultra-low power embedded hardware solutions that enhance signal quality and enable artificial intelligence (AI) analytics. The company focuses on providing innovative Edge-AI solutions that allow system-on-chip (SoC) makers to incorporate high-quality neural signal processing and analytics into their products through IP-Core technology, followed by Chiplets. They aim to empower their clients with advanced capabilities to improve performance and functionality in various applications.

Carlin Consumer Health is a company focused on the healthcare industry, particularly in managing and promoting over-the-counter health and beauty brands. They leverage long-standing connections with major and regional retailers to ensure that their brands receive the attention necessary to succeed in a competitive market.
